<BlogLayout
  title="ASA: The Filament Nobody Talks About (That You Should Be Using)"
  description="ASA is the most underrated filament in desktop 3D printing. UV-stable, tough, weather-resistant — and almost nobody uses it. Here's why that should change."
  datePublished="2025-09-05"
